        "description": "Gets PayFast payment URL. Replace {{orderId}} with orderId from TEST 1.\n\nInstructions:\n1. Run TEST 1 first\n2. Copy the orderId from response\n3. Set variable: orderId = your_order_id\n4. Run this test\n5. Copy payfastUrl for payment"
      },
      "response": []
    },
